{"tid":646260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林盛斌湊4子女踢晒腳","createTime":"2018-04-29T01:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T02:39:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6203de2bb47b982035a3d7d54543417cf5f141a6","tid":646260,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"藝人林盛斌（Bob）育有三女一子，上個月Bob透露細仔林道申（Jaye）因患上「人類間質肺炎病毒」需要入院，上星期Bob出席活動時表示囝囝因為發燒要進出醫院。昨日Bob透過社交網發長文，透露太太出外公幹，由他負責照顧四個小朋友，十分頻撲，他留言說：「成件事好似招募面試啲題目咁，如果有一日，細佬突然發高燒，大家姐同二家姐爭玩具鬧緊交，三家姐又喺度扭計喪喊，工人姐姐又忙緊，最爆嘅係媽咪出差唔喺香港，呢一刻，爸爸，你會點做？ 幾日內，來回醫院十幾次，終於返屋企了。」Bob此時感到太太的偉大，表示：「最超級無敵的太太，依家諗番，都真係要畀個叻自己。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E7%9B%9B%E6%96%8C%E6%B9%8A4%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E8%B8%A2%E6%99%92%E8%85%B3-214500730.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E7%259B%259B%25E6%2596%258C%25E6%25B9%258A4%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E6%2599%2592%25E8%2585%25B3-214500730.html&d=rkM8dvoGC4zeQMu%2F0UsLqb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ea716069\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E7%9B%9B%E6%96%8C%E6%B9%8A4%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E8%B8%A2%E6%99%92%E8%85%B3-214500730.html</a>"},{"pid":"66c6a2d47558a84f9ab3268a2f2b08a6dbece0c8","tid":646260,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"父債子好快會還"},{"pid":"1f46a34864fe07b8521bdb0811c02b56db64a03d","tid":646260,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"追仔正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae68d7d79021e248da74273b45792263ee727ba","tid":646260,"uid":84013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"養到生多幾個都好<br />\n提高出生率"},{"pid":"314eb3e2bbe6c3ac9c232298f60835b084fb2397","tid":646260,"uid":8810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"<span sty